{"tid":2499251,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"幼貓疑似腹膜炎！","createTime":"2021-04-21T17:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T03:53:41.000Z","uid":369954,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6334ae7d3fbcf96c02ae34af34d7225dfa7d3479","tid":2499251,"uid":369954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T17:48:18.000Z","msg":"前個幾個禮拜因為有肚屙問題所以帶咗它去睇獸醫，本來食藥都好地地，開頭食都好返好多，突然有日開始就無哂精神，又唔肯食嘢，開頭以為它係因為藥物食欲不振<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知它情況越嚟越差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開始行路無力、唔肯食嘢，平時明明跳跳紮，已經拿拿聲想帶佢睇急症/門診，門診又要等好耐，好多急症診又唔收佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好啦，終於搵到一間24小時急症，隔咗一兩日，佢已經連行路都困難，行一步抖兩步，醫生幫佢驗血之後同我地講它情況好唔樂觀，咩血球、神經出哂事，仲懷疑它係腹膜炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生話有兩個選擇一係同它磁力共振，睇下咩病，但check到咩絕症都係醫唔返，另一個就係食藥睇有無好轉，無好轉嘅應該都要安樂死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明它健康嗰陣咁精靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce800af54c96f920245179b851a1b54737d7ee6d","tid":2499251,"uid":234120,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T17:49:28.000Z","msg":"好cute <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望貓貓會冇事"},{"pid":"dcee889b4deb5c715ae4bb662aef1a59598bab84","tid":2499251,"uid":23682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T17:50:37.000Z","msg":"去fb揾fip腹膜炎group<br />\n開post，有義工會教你點揾藥"},{"pid":"0f0292e4906394265b2791c936a7b3c43df06104","tid":2499251,"uid":57439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"腹膜炎的話, 亯請google 441"},{"pid":"e69c4469c87ec30a21d5648662a2529f391ed7c9","tid":2499251,"uid":23682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score